---
title: Risotto alla Tex-Mex with Corn, Bell Pepper, and Pepitas
description: We’re not food purists by any means: we say, if something tastes good, why not run with it? Which is exactly the case in this transcontinental, mixed-up, mashed-up risotto that features some distinctly non-Italian flavors. Jalapeño, corn, and Monterey jack cheese give it a Texan edge, adding some larger-than-life personality to the extra-creamy grains of rice.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/tex-mex-risotto-2d5a735e.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/tex-mex-risotto-8d05ce7c.pdf
time required: 50 minutes
